            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae <supplied reason="lost">Re</supplied>ginae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Com</abbr><ex>inius</ex></expan> Q<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>intus <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublico</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>pon</abbr><ex>tifex</ex></expan> et q<expan><ex>uin</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>uennalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> et Anto<lb break="no" n="4"/>nia Valentina eius <lb n="5"/>pro salute Claudi<lb break="no" n="6"/>ae Valentinae </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>templ</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> a solo fecerunt
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): SIRIS: abweichende Angabe des Wechsel des Inschriftfeldes (Z. 4/5 statt 6/7); Ardevan: Z. 2: Comin(ius); Z. 4/5 u. 5/6: keine Angabe der Zeilenfälle.</p>
            </div>
